Development server
==================
This system runs on vagrant & puppet. Please do not
change configuration files in /vagrant/environments
or you may corrupt your installation.

Connect to host with dev.loc
----------------------------
Please add the following line to the hosts file of
the vagrant host (you will need admin privs):
192.168.56.150 dev.loc

Mac:  /private/etc/hosts
WIN:  C:\Windows\System32\drivers\etc\hosts

Update PHP configuration
------------------------
Please update your box' php config with:
date.timezone = Europe/Berlin

...in files:
/etc/php5/apache2/php.ini
/etc/php5/cli/php.ini

Have fun!